  "The maximum amount you can borrow, even when conditions shift significantly": "",
  "The total interest paid on a loan, based on conventional assumptions about formula": "",
  "The down payment amount for a mortgage, especially during periods of significant change": "",
  "The fixed periodic payment needed to fully pay off a loan or reach a savings goal over a specified period": "",
  "The PMT formula calculates the equal periodic payment required to pay off a present value (loan) or accumulate a future value (savings), given an interest rate and number of periods.": "",
